text: Lamington is an unincorporated community located within Bedminster Township, in Somerset County, New Jersey, United States.Locality Search, State of New Jersey. Accessed June 9, 2016. The Lamington Historic District, which includes the Presbyterian Church and the Lamington Black Cemetery, was added to the National Register of Historic Places in 1984. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in New Jersey
title: Lamington, New Jersey
